---
title: 7-Layer Dip Avocado Toasts with Tomato, Refried Black Beans & Cheddar
description: Yes, it finally happened: Our chefs just turned your favorite dip into a 10-minute lunchtime treat! Layer toasted sourdough bread with creamy refried black beans, guacamole, juicy tomato, green pepper, tangy cheddar, and sour cream, then drizzle with as much hot sauce as you like. Dip, dip, olé!
